HEADWORD: Chalcography
<hw>Chal*cog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>chalko`s</grk> copper, brass + <ets>-graphy</ets>.]</ety> <def>The
